* 2010年，《[[中国新闻周刊|中国新闻周刊]]》评为“十年影响力之环保人物”。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://news.sina.com.cn/c/sd/2009-12-25/171219339517.shtml |title = 中国新闻周刊十年影响力之环保人物 |publisher = 新浪新闻中心 |accessdate = 2010-02-27 |archive-date = 2011-11-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111112052126/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/sd/2009-12-25/171219339517.shtml |dead-url = no }}</ref>

